				<p>My views on medical tourism and it&#8217;s health risks are rather mixed. I had one friend who received heart surgery in India with no complaints. Another friend had plastic surgery in Thailand and didn&#8217;t enjoy it. It&#8217;s true Medical Tourism is only for rich &#8211; &#8220;Medical tourism is like five star hotels&#8221;. Nice Article, thanks.</p>
