			<section class="comment-content comment">
				<p>I agree with the article that the hospitals used by medical tourists are like 5 star hotels. That is unfortunate for Indian healthcare. On the other hand, the investments that mainly private companies are currently making in Indian healthcare are tremendous. This combined with wages in society increasing dramatically and the rise of health insurance products will hopefully improve the situation of Indian locals.</p>
